Package com.github.protobufel.grammar Description

Via its ProtoFiles class, provides the ability to :
  1. parse .proto files off files, URI resources, and texts
  2. add FileDescriptorProto(-s) to build FileDecsriptor(-s) from
  3. build the canonical FileDecsriptorProtos and FileDecsriptors based on the above input
See Also:
Examples.java, ProtoFiles
